<doc f='llvm/lldb/source/Breakpoint/Watchpoint.cpp' l='221'>// Within StopInfo.cpp, we purposely turn on the ephemeral mode right before
// temporarily disable the watchpoint in order to perform possible watchpoint
// actions without triggering further watchpoint events. After the temporary
// disabled watchpoint is enabled, we then turn off the ephemeral mode.</doc>
